        <property propertyId="67f102e2-9cb6-4d20-aa16-bf74d8a03326" amount="1.0" isDefiningValue="true" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
          <name xml:lang="en">wet mass</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        </property>
        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Unknown

The addition of the consumption volumes in the US in 2002 (from USGS, 2002 Pesticide use Maps) of the pyridazine-compounds norflurazon, pyridate has been used to estimate the production volumes of this type of pesticide in the Europe. For that, it has been extrapolated to a Global production mix using the ha of Arable land and Permanent crops of US versus the ha of Arable land and Permanent crops in the Europe in 2002 (299/179 million ha; FAOSTAT).</productionVolumeComment>
